      • setKeyNameAliasMap

        public void setKeyNameAliasMap(Map<String,String> keyNameAliasMap)
        Set the Signature KeyName alias lookup map. It is used on the receiving side for signature. It maps a KeyName to a key alias - so it allows us to associate a (e.g.) key alias in a keystore with a given KeyName contained in a KeyInfo structure of the Signature.
